            "text": {
                "header": "Using Matterhorn",
                "body": "<p>Now that you have all the Matterhorn details, the last thing you need to know is how to use it!</p><p>Matterhorn reservations begin with a Salesforce opportunity and a conversation with your pod. Make sure you’re all on the same page about the media plan recommendations for this client. Afterwards, use the <b>Create Sponsorship</b> button in the opportunity to request a Matterhorn reservation.</p><p>Check out this <a target='_blank' href='https://www.brainshark.com/pandoramedia/vu?pi=zHizDtaeoz6hX2z0&r3f1=b882fcafa3e7e3e4fce88de9f6bebcb8bffefb82e7a9bdf3bfaaede88dedb9b6bcbfbfb5ea85e5e1e4edfcfab4e88bf8f4bebcb8bffefb82e7a9bdf2a4a4f6ecc4dae09ed4dd'>video</a> to walk you through the Matterhorn user interface</p>",
                "class": "align-right|align-left|align-center|align-center-wide"
